10.4 Expiry on termination of BS debtor agreement
:SKRSLUT.
.br
If the BS debtor agreement with &BANKNAVN. is terminated, all BS
mandates under the BS debtor agreement will expire see clause 12.2.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:SWISS8.
:FED.
10.5 If the creditor ceases to use Betalingsservice
:SKRSLUT.
.br
If the creditor ceases to use Betalingsservice, the customer's
BS mandate with the creditor automatically expires.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:SWISS8.
:FED.
10.6 Effect of cancellation and expiry
:SKRSLUT.
.br
If a BS mandate is cancelled or has expired, the creditor may no
longer collect payments from the customer. Any payments notified
but not yet executed will not be executed.
The customer's Betalingsservice prenotification will show cancelled and
expired BS mandates.
.sp 5mm
.kp off
.kp on
