12. Termination of the BS debtor agreement by &BANKNAVN.
.sp 3mm
:SWISS8.
:FED.
12.1 Notification
:SKRSLUT.
.br
:SWISS8.
&BANKNAVN. may terminate the BS debtor agreement by giving at least two
months' notice.
.br
&BANKNAVN. may terminate the agreement without notice in the event of a
material breach of contract on the customer's part. &BANKNAVN. will inform
the customer in writing of the reason for terminating the agreement. An
example of a material breach would be if the customer failed on several
occasions to ensure there were sufficient funds in the customer's account
(see clause 7.2).
