13. &BANKNAVN.'s failure to meet obligations
:SKRSLUT.
.sp 3mm
:SWISS8.
If Betalingsservice does not execute a payment because &BANKNAVN. suspends
payments or goes bankrupt, the creditor is entitled to collect payment from
the customer in another way.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
