16. Changes to debtor conditions
.sp 3mm
:SWISS8.
:FED.
16.1 Notification
:SKRSLUT.
.br
Changes of these conditions to the customer's disadvantage are subject to
two months' notification. Other changes may take effect without notice. The
customer will be notified of changes by email, ordinary letter, through the
customer's online banking system or another channel.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:FED.
16.2 Approval
:SKRSLUT.
.br
:SWISS8.
The customer is assumed to have approved the notified changes unless the
customer informs &BANKNAVN. that he or she does not wish to be bound by the
revised conditions. If the customer cannot approve the changes, the
customer's BS debtor agreement will terminate as from the day when the
changes take effect.
