17. Law and jurisdiction
.sp 3mm
:SWISS8.
This agreement is covered by the rules valid in Greenland.
Disputes may be brought before the Consumer Compliant Committe in
Greenland as well as before the ordinary courts where The BANK of
Greenlands's competent court is the judicial venue.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:SWISS8.
Disputes relating to PBS's role as a payment service provider may be
brought before the Danish Financial Supervisory Authority.
